---
title: Baja Barramundi with Turmeric Quinoa, Salsa Fresca & Lime Crema
description: Salsa fresca is our favorite way to channel warm-weather vibes all year round. It’s juicy and tangy with a touch of heat, making it the perfect complement to crispy, turmeric-and-cumin-spiced barramundi. The fillets are served on top of steamy quinoa and blanketed in lime crema and said salsa. No matter the temperature, one bite of this delicious dish will make everything feel a whole lot sunnier
